1.22.name: wordpress/application-maker-crm-edition
1.22.description:
BLUE ORIGAMI CRM FREE VERSION (Formerly Application Maker | CRM Edition) - A product from 15 Green leaves

Version: 1.4.3 | CRM | Last update date: 30th JULY 2013. And more releases to come soon.

Last update 30th JULY 2013: V1.4.3 fix a bug with the users list field type in the Contacts module post edit form.

Last update 29th JULY 2013: V1.4.2 Updated the Mailing list/Newsletters modules

Last update 27th JULY 2013: MAJOR UPDATE, V1.4.1 is the now BLUE ORIGAMI CRM FREE EDITION, with a lot of updates all along the system. And this is the FREE version of the pluign that will now have a PRO paying (cheap) VERSION.

For more informations, we have now done a basic simple plugin minisite specially to support this plugin: http://apmcrm2013.15gl.net

And about the PRO VERSION, find more on http://apm
